title: Jade James - Applying for Passion (Capture, Inc. #2).epub
description:
Applying for Passion
Jack invests as part owner of Capture Inc. with intentions of treating it strictly as a business investment. But after a heated interaction with the lovely Isabel a wedding reception, Jack finds his resolve not just tempted but broken--because Isabel contacts Capture Inc. for some fantasy play and he's helpless to deny her anything.
Isabel had given up ever finding someone for her until Jack more than caught her eye at her sister's wedding reception. Since then, Jack is all she can think about. Determined to get her man, Isabel goes after him through Capture Inc. But when a stalker steps up his game, she's placed under Jack's care. Then Isabel realizes Jack's more than a lust interest. He's the person she's meant to be with forever.
